data.title: Live in Hiroshima (2003) * amazing high pitched vocals by Timo Kotipelto *

An amazing performance! All 5 guys in a great shape! And super Kotipelto performance of "Find Your Own Voice", thought impossible to sing live! But there it went: perfect.
